org.eclipse.symphony.common.topology.ui
Interface TopologyListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
TopologyListenerImpl
public interface TopologyListener
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Topology Listener'.

The following features are supported:

  • Presentation Topology
  • Node To J3D Object Map
  • Topology
  • Java3d Scene Root
  • Node To Node Presentation Map

See Also:
UiPackage.getTopologyListener()
